{
  "texts": [
    "Consequently, the integration of blockchain into the legal system cannot be unequivocally deemed either entirely beneficial or detrimental.",
    "A foundational survey conducted by Joshi et al. (2018) provides a comprehensive overview of security and privacy challenges in blockchain technology.",
    "This survey categorizes challenges into various dimensions, including consensus algorithms, privacy concerns, and smart contract vulnerabilities.",
    "Serving as a baseline for subsequent discussions, this work offers a holistic view of security issues in blockchain.",
    "Wylde et al. (2022) further explores the intersection of cybersecurity, data privacy, and blockchain technology, emphasizing the evolving nature of this relationship."
  ]
}